body:
HELP!!

OK, So I’m currently writing something that will be coming out soon, however, I need some help!

If there is anyone that has been pregnant could you please give me a message, I just want to write accurately. I’ve been doing some research but I would like some information from people with different stories etc!!

All I would need is:

- Feelings and experiences during each trimester

- Struggles throughout the pregnancy

- Things that helped you throughout the pregnancy

- Cravings etc

If you can please help, send me a message, you can do it on anon if you wish and feel free to go in to as much detail as you feel comfortable with.

Thank you, lots of love

- x
